project.name: ART-004: Pipeline - Metrics Project
project.description: Advanced Persistent Threat - Mission Aware Metrics Project.

attributes.purpose: “Black Monday” Scenario - Attack on Oil Pipeline Pumps::::Russia’s largeness in natural gas and oil exporter by volume has impending economic downturn, causing rise in unsteadiness and leading to malicious cyberattacks to gain more control in NG and oil export.::::There is a cyberattack on Saudi Aramco Riyadh & Yanbu Baiji and SPC refineries: 1) Reports false flow rates, pressure, temperature. 2) Russia offers world‐class cyber security services to all three countries, but installs backdoor measures.::::Short term effects show yield of oil decrease by 6.2M b/d, with overall 10% decrease in global oil market for 3 years and price of oil skyrockets.::::Long term has covert cyber control over OPEC control systems.
